Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.95,0:00:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That she-gorilla who wears shorts year-round?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a weird sneeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bio...hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Combat medics!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.50,0:00:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gorilla germs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who you callin' a gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's on the warpath!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here some lemonade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mom said that vitamin C's good for colds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like I have a cold!\NGorillas don't catch colds!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a gorilla, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a girl, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All better now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:00:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, entrance exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was cramming all through winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll try for a lower-ranked school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He got early admission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.35,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wednesday January 11th
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got a Grade B!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.11,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}National Unified Junior High Mock Exam\NEntrance Exam Results - By School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can do it if you try, Tsubaki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna go brag to him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:54.29,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Music Preparation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I'll only be a third wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're checking in, right?\N My Kaori-chan's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, just because\Nyou made it through the prelims,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,don't think you can afford\Nto get cocky and loiter here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go practice, you loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the one who told me to stop by!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today at school, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This one girl said she's\N going to an all-girls school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess all-girls schools\Nare kind of glamorous, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'd fit right in, Kaori-chan!\NAt an all-girls school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kao-chan likes Watari, you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:03:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watari-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watari-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A girl who likes my best friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a voyeur, and a substitute,\N and a baggage handler,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and a pianist, and an accompanist, and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not Watari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom's gonna blow a fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do whatever it takes\Nso that she'll let me keep her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mom likes animals, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't dry yourself off, you'll catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find Chelsea anywhere.\NNot at the junkyard or under the bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she's out here in this cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I couldn't say a word,\Nand I knew that my mom would get rid of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chelsea still might have survived, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Puppet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The human metronome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a soulless puppet\Nthat my mother created.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, you do have a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got all these good qualities - a ton!\NI know you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like right now, you're running around\Nlike your life depended on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:06:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that because you regret it?\NBecause you want to tell Chelsea you're sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You do too have a soul, Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that you're good at hiding it.\NSo good, you can't even find it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to find it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you won't lose your way,\Nso you won't have regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay by your side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I know everything there is\N to know about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the hospital today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She orders me\Nto check in with her regularly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then she says if I have time to go,\NI should practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watari came to see Kao-chan, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's gonna rain.\NLet's head home today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can smell the rain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, here it comes! It's coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I wish it would just snow instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd only wish that until it piled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the snow had its own flavor,\Nwe'd have world peace, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If our tap water was lemonade,\Nit would eradicate the common cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Talking like we always do...\NThe banter... joking around...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suddenly having to take shelter from the rain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a cute handkerchief you're using, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A boy right next to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're like a girl, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're a girl, Tsubaki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you're a girl, Tsubaki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Liar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know you didn't want to. To go see Kao-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because Watari was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't think we should get in their way.\NWhen it could just be the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! You just can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts to see Kao-chan and Watari\Nlaughing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why you're avoiding her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can tell right away when you're holding back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like you stayed by my side,\NI want to stay by yours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can read you like a book, Kousei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You like Kao-chan, Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miwa said something once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The moment I met him, my life changed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything I saw, everything I heard,\Neverything I felt... all the scenery around me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It started to take on color.\NMy world began to sparkle."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Friend A!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kao-chan likes Watari, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She always did, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As if she'd ever give you a second look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to girls,\Nif you're up against Watari,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have a snowball's chance in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Liar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You said you'd stay by my side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can tell right away when you're holding back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't know the first thing about me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you liar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've never once thought of me as a girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kao-chan likes Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...have no choice but to love me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How's that for taking the plunge? Screw you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I took the first step!\NI made him see me as a girl!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I went through a lot of suffering.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you can suffer, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suffer, suffer, suffer,\Nand think about me constantly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It finally started.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what's gonna happen now?\NMy heart's about to burst.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The rain in winter feels so good.\NIt tastes like lemonade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time I exist in...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...just started flowing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted. Let's go home.\NDon't you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just got caught in the rain.\NDon't worry about me, just pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna chase them down, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen between you and Arima?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You trying to kill me?! Idiot Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for saying\N something freaky like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! It's so obvious.\NYou were so aiming for the music room...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you two fight again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:12:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just gave Kousei a good kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, he was limping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Imbecile! Smartass! Four Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Suffer some more for all I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I ever gonna show up to root\Nfor you again! Live a lonely life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't yell at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think about me more, dummy Kousei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reach him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reach him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My shot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you... have no choice but to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that all about, I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was just messing around, right?\NBut for Tsubaki to make that kind of joke...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's like a kid brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enigmas... girls are such enigmas...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.33,Menacing,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seto
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you into this or not? You don't have\Nmuch time before the finals in February!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a cop-out of a performance. How cliché.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did he wet his pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're up against top talents\Nloaded with grit and passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you'll be going on to high school here,\Nor leaving the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how you do in this competition\Nwill decide your future as a pianist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Better man up,\Nyou're standing at the crossroads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have to come to the hospital anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The final's coming up soon, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you have time to come here,\Nyou should go over the sheet music.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pound even one more phrase into your head!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So anyway, bye bye now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?!\NShe's the one who told me to check in regularly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's so selfish! So irresponsible! So outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it... something I did?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I shouldn't have\Neaten that chocolate bar at the hospital.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I don't say anything when I'm there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I pissed her off\Nby talking about Aiza-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I stop checking in...\Nthen I won't have a reason to see you anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.42,MSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori Miyazono
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Look! There's a plane in the sky!\NIt's a night flight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amazing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? You can see it, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow, the sky's connected, then, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.86,0:15:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. Something wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The plane crosses the sea of stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a cat, you silently creep up to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You told me not to come to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.25,0:16:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I didn't say I wouldn't call you.\NIt's flying really low, even though it's night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She bombards me from an unexpected angle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm dumbfounded, always following you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop by again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you don't have to.\NYou know you don't have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A lump of steel, like a shooting star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just seeing the same sky as you\Nmakes familiar scenery look different.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swing between hope\Nand despair at your slightest gesture,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and my heart starts to play a melody.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of feeling is this again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do they call this kind of feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think it's probably...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...called loved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure this is what they call love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a sports scholarship,\Nso no surprises there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They told me to report\Nto the soccer team starting in March.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the bottom of the heap all over again.\NGonna be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but still, who knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You hated it whenever I asked you\Nto come with me to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was avoiding her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever I compare myself to Watari,\NI always get depressed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You like Kao-chan, Kousei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really like Miyazono.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so you're finally gonna\Nduke it out with me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get Dr. Katagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Kaori-chan's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on! The doctor will be here soon, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyazono, are you with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get better in no time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take a deep breath, Ms. Miyazono!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyazono! Ms. Miyazono!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyazono, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyazono!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyazono, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyazono, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyazono!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyazono! Stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're treating her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go home today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:07.34,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totsuhara University Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?! Hello?! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get me that X-ray. Check its blood type.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was pretty much beyond saving\Nwhen he got hit. I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you think you'll be able to forget?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You come, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your hands are happy to be touching mine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm glad it's you.{\i0}
